content:
when Russia invaded Ukraine, crude oil was $99 a barrel. 

today, it's fallen back down to $99 barrel. 

the day Russia invaded, US motorists were paying $3.61 at the pump 

today, they're paying $4.30. 

how the hell does press just ignore this story????
